#

Savory Beef and Black Bean Burrito

$12.99
750 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

High ProteinLow Carb

Tags:

BeefBurritoComfort Food

Description

A hearty burrito filled with seasoned beef, black beans, and a zesty salsa that packs a flavorful punch!

Ingredients

  • Ground beef: 1 lb
  • Black beans: 1 can (15 oz) drained
  • Tortilla wraps: 4 large
  • Cheddar cheese: 1 cup shredded
  • Sour cream: 1/2 cup
  • Salsa: 1 cup
  • Olive oil: 2 tbsp
  • Cumin: 1 tsp
  • Chili powder: 1 tsp
  • Garlic powder: 1/2 tsp
  • Salt: to taste
  • Black pepper: to taste
